{"tid":879224,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(求分析)她最近追我FB po","createTime":"2018-10-27T17:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T20:35:46.000Z","uid":45255,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dc074705eeef4a2999d18787a476fae0f6e60b4c","tid":879224,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T17:50:12.000Z","msg":"先利申一下背景:<br />\n<br />\n同事兼舊同事關係，不過古今都不同Department兼隔好遠，冇乜碰到面<br />\n<br />\n心目中佢at least中上樣，文靜type，工作時好專注。暫時知佢個人喜愛旅遊尤其日本。不過佢FB好靜，甚少update同畀like之類，可能只係CD Rom嗰款<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事源今月頭小弟首次歐遊 (丹麥 &amp; 法羅群島) 旅途上自己FB每日都貼一至兩po分享行程同風景相，色括放埋上Story度(即係限時24個鐘)<br />\n<br />\n重點就喺Story度，我留意到佢咁耐以嚟第一次睇我Story的相，而且喺我po嘅第一張就看。之後我日日貼的Story相佢都差不多有睇，應該似係追緊我嘅旅行po. Story上有少量自拍，加少許chok樣，例如抱起隻羊仔扮想食咗佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然佢仍冇任何comment / like之類反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講返，其實佢曾經喺現時公司度撩我傾偈，不過當時我自己怕醜到除咗淨係答是非題就再冇講嘢，可能已比咗個壞印象佢，覺我太cool，好毒etc.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲可以分析下佢現時係點睇我，我又有冇機會可以再主動搵佢交談。偈旅遊嘢會不會可以啱咀形諸如此類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924f51670a0be8be6bb7195497c73f5a4f264f92","tid":879224,"uid":157510,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T17:54:34.000Z","msg":"睇個story就咁多ff<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不嬲ig睇story除非係特別長否則就手指公㩒到底"},{"pid":"9d27d6ed70d5181eec9873702696cfa8a78caaa1","tid":879224,"uid":189053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T17:55:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d278e433bb919c96d5a562e3eda7a870fb689e9b","tid":879224,"uid":147856,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T17:59:26.000Z","msg":"2018年仲Facebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716ecd6057e302aea8e438aed9231b0219cdbdfa","tid":879224,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"924f51670a0be8be6bb7195497c73f5a4f264f92","tid":879224,"uid":157510,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T17:54:34.000Z","msg":"睇個story就咁多ff<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不嬲ig睇story除非係特別長否則就手指公㩒到底"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T18:04:26.000Z","msg":"FB, not IG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f606b475378b11234601bec19100e04bf7b32855","tid":879224,"uid":192832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T18:06:24.000Z","msg":"人地8掛下炸 on9"},{"pid":"5bab6477bb47e766b8ca42c995755a56452a15ef","tid":879224,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d27d6ed70d5181eec9873702696cfa8a78caaa1","tid":879224,"uid":189053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T17:55:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T18:06:32.000Z","msg":"所以我話佢以前從未睇過我貼嘅FB story, 到我今次旅行就開始睇兼差不多睇曬我隨後貼嘅相"},{"pid":"277f03ee8806901d4a994d7327516e97d96c7371","tid":879224,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f606b475378b11234601bec19100e04bf7b32855","tid":879224,"uid":192832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T18:06:24.000Z","msg":"人地8掛下炸 on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T18:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7996578ef904ae9beb90b63e5d4481f8d09d6d7","tid":879224,"uid":182195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T19:09:33.000Z","msg":"其實都係睇下個story姐&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾廿歲人唔好咁多幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" clas